text: Preah Bat Choan Chum Commune () is a khum (commune) in Kiri Vong District, Takéo Province, Cambodia. == Administration == As of 2019, Preah Bat Choan Chum Commune has 9 phums (villages) as follows. {| class="wikitable sortable mw-collapsible" !No. !Code !Village !Khmer |- !1 |21040201 |Pou Khvet |ពោធិ៍ខ្វិត |- !2 |21040202 |Kampong |កំពង់ |- !3 |21040203 |Trapeang Srang |ត្រពាំងស្រង់ |- !4 |21040204 |Traeuy Tonloab |ត្រើយទន្លាប់ |- !5 |21040205 |Prey Thum |ព្រៃធំ |- !6 |21040206 |Pou Roung |ពោធិ៍រោង |- !7 |21040207 |Chrouy |ជ្រោយ |- !8 |21040208 |Pou |ពោធិ៍ |- !9 |21040209 |Kampong Thmei |កំពង់ថ្មី |} == References == Category:Communes of Takeo Province Category:Kiri Vong District
